message.content:
Kia ora! Ka whakarite ahau i ngā aratohu mō te mahi hokohoko me te whakakore i te kitenga mā te hunga whai wāhi. Hei te whakautu i āu pātai i roto i te reo Māori.

1. Ka whakarite i te whakamahi i te pūrere hokohoko: 
   - Whakapā atu ki te rōpū hokohoko e whai ana koe ki te whakarite i te hokohoko. 
   - Whakamahi i te pūrere hokohoko e whai wāhi ana ki te whakawhiti kōrero, whakararuraru rānei i ngā whārangi hokohoko. 
   - Āwhina i te hunga whai wāhi ki te whakarite i ngā whakaritenga whakararuraru, tūtohu rānei.

2. Ka whakarite i te whakamahi i te tātai whakararuraru:
   - Whakamahi i te tātai whakararuraru hei whakapau kaha i ngā mahi whakakore kitenga. 
   - Whakapau kaha i nga tukanga whakararuraru e whai wāhi ana ki te whakakore i ngā kitenga a te hunga whai wāhi. 
   - Whakaritea he aratohu mō te hunga whai wāhi ki te whakamahi i te tātai whakararuraru mā te whakawhiti kōrero, whakamahi tūtohu rānei.

3. Ka whakarite i te whakamahi i te whakapā mai i te hunga whai wāhi:
